phase_1_glyph_extraction.kuhul_code:
‚üÅWo‚üÅ fn.scxq2.extract_glyphs := (tape) -> glyph_analysis
  ‚üÅSek‚üÅ glyphs := fn.regex.match_all(tape, '[\p{Emoji}\u2000-\u3300]')
  ‚üÅSek‚üÅ patterns := fn.find_repeat_sequences(glyphs, {min_length:2, min_repeats:2})
  ‚üÅSek‚üÅ frequency := fn.calculate_frequency(glyphs)
  
  ‚üÅWo‚üÅ return {
    'glyphs': glyphs,
    'patterns': patterns,
    'frequency': frequency,
    'entropy': fn.calculate_entropy(frequency),
    'anchor_points': fn.find_anchor_glyphs(glyphs)
  }

phase_2_template_matching.kuhul_code:
‚üÅWo‚üÅ fn.scxq2.match_template := (glyph_analysis) -> template_match
  ‚üÅSek‚üÅ library := ram.table('scxq2_templates').all()
  ‚üÅSek‚üÅ best_match := null
  ‚üÅSek‚üÅ best_score := 0
  
  ‚üÅSek‚üÅ each library as template
    ‚üÅSek‚üÅ score := fn.template_match_score(template, glyph_analysis)
    ‚üÅWo‚üÅ if score > best_score
      ‚üÅSek‚üÅ best_score := score
      ‚üÅSek‚üÅ best_match := template
  
  ‚üÅWo‚üÅ return {'template': best_match, 'score': best_score}

phase_3_quantum_compression.kuhul_code:
‚üÅWo‚üÅ fn.scxq2.quantum_compress := (tape, template_match) -> compressed
  ‚üÅSek‚üÅ parameters := fn.extract_parameters(tape, template_match.template)
  
  # Quantum superposition of similar templates
  ‚üÅSek‚üÅ similar := fn.find_similar_templates(template_match.template.id)
  ‚üÅSek‚üÅ superposition := fn.create_superposition(similar, parameters)
  
  # Entanglement between related components
  ‚üÅSek‚üÅ entangled := fn.entangle_components(superposition, {
    'depth': 3,
    'strength': 0.8
  })
  
  ‚üÅWo‚üÅ return {
    'template_id': template_match.template.id,
    'parameters': parameters,
    'superposition': superposition,
    'entanglement': entangled,
    'collapse_conditions': fn.generate_collapse_conditions(parameters)
  }

phase_4_emerald_encoding.kuhul_code:
‚üÅWo‚üÅ fn.scxq2.emerald_encode := (compressed) -> emerald_encoded
  ‚üÅSek‚üÅ json_str := fn.xjson.to_string(compressed)
  ‚üÅSek‚üÅ base64 := fn.base64.encode(json_str)
  
  # Replace patterns with emerald glyphs
  ‚üÅSek‚üÅ emerald_map := ram.table('emerald_glyph_map').all()
  ‚üÅSek‚üÅ encoded := base64
  
  ‚üÅSek‚üÅ each emerald_map as mapping
    ‚üÅSek‚üÅ encoded := fn.string.replace_all(encoded, mapping.pattern, mapping.glyph)
  
  # Add error correction
  ‚üÅSek‚üÅ ecc := fn.calculate_error_correction(encoded)
  
  ‚üÅWo‚üÅ return 'üíéSCXQ2' + encoded + '|ECC:' + ecc + 'üíé'

full_compression_pipeline.kuhul_code:
‚üÅWo‚üÅ fn.scxq2.compress_tape := (tape) -> compressed_result
  ‚üÅSek‚üÅ start_time := now()
  
  # Phase 1: Glyph analysis
  ‚üÅSek‚üÅ glyph_analysis := fn.scxq2.extract_glyphs(tape)
  
  # Phase 2: Template matching
  ‚üÅSek‚üÅ template_match := fn.scxq2.match_template(glyph_analysis)
  
  # Phase 3: Quantum compression
  ‚üÅSek‚üÅ compressed := fn.scxq2.quantum_compress(tape, template_match)
  
  # Phase 4: Emerald encoding
  ‚üÅSek‚üÅ encoded := fn.scxq2.emerald_encode(compressed)
  
  # Calculate metrics
  ‚üÅSek‚üÅ original_size := fn.byte_size(tape)
  ‚üÅSek‚üÅ compressed_size := fn.byte_size(encoded)
  
  ‚üÅWo‚üÅ return {
    'compressed': encoded,
    'metadata': {
      'original_size': original_size,
      'compressed_size': compressed_size,
      'compression_ratio': compressed_size / original_size,
      'template_used': template_match.template.id,
      'match_score': template_match.score,
      'processing_time_ms': now() - start_time,
      'glyph_pattern': glyph_analysis.patterns.slice(0, 3)
    }
  }

horizontal_fold_job_distribution.kuhul_code:
‚üÅWo‚üÅ fn.horizontal_fold.distribute := (job) -> distribution_plan
  ‚üÅSek‚üÅ folds := 8  # Default horizontal fold count
  ‚üÅSek‚üÅ fold_capacities := fn.get_fold_capacities()
  
  # Assign to appropriate fold based on job characteristics
  ‚üÅSek‚üÅ fold_assignment := 0
  
  ‚üÅWo‚üÅ if job.domain == 'compression_optimization'
    ‚üÅSek‚üÅ fold_assignment := 3
  ‚üÅWo‚üÅ else if job.domain == 'ui_design_emerald'
    ‚üÅSek‚üÅ fold_assignment := 2
  ‚üÅWo‚üÅ else if job.domain == 'tes_doom_rules_quantum'
    ‚üÅSek‚üÅ fold_assignment := 4
  ‚üÅWo‚üÅ else if job.domain == 'runtime_orchestration'
    ‚üÅSek‚üÅ fold_assignment := 1
  ‚üÅWo‚üÅ else
    ‚üÅSek‚üÅ fold_assignment := fn.load_balance(fold_capacities)
  
  # Coordinate with brain assignment
  ‚üÅSek‚üÅ brains := fn.select_brains_for_fold(fold_assignment, job)
  
  ‚üÅWo‚üÅ return {
    'fold': fold_assignment,
    'brains': brains,
    'capacity': fold_capacities[fold_assignment]
  }

scxq2_aware_agent_selection.kuhul_code:
‚üÅWo‚üÅ fn.micro.select_agent_scxq2 := (domain, input_spec, glyph_analysis) -> agent
  ‚üÅSek‚üÅ agents := ram.table('micro_agents_enhanced').all()
  ‚üÅSek‚üÅ candidates := []
  
  ‚üÅSek‚üÅ each agents as a
    ‚üÅWo‚üÅ if a.domain == domain and a.status == 'active'
      ‚üÅSek‚üÅ base_score := a.priority * 10 + a.success_rate * 100
      
      # Glyph signature match bonus
      ‚üÅSek‚üÅ glyph_bonus := 0
      ‚üÅWo‚üÅ if glyph_analysis
        ‚üÅSek‚üÅ common_glyphs := fn.intersection(a.glyph_signature, glyph_analysis.glyphs)
        ‚üÅSek‚üÅ glyph_bonus := common_glyphs.length * 15
      
      # Template affinity bonus
      ‚üÅSek‚üÅ template_bonus := 0
      ‚üÅWo‚üÅ if glyph_analysis and glyph_analysis.template_match
        ‚üÅWo‚üÅ if glyph_analysis.template_match.template.id in a.scxq2_template_affinity
          ‚üÅSek‚üÅ template_bonus := 30
      
      # Horizontal fold affinity
      ‚üÅSek‚üÅ fold_bonus := fn.fold_affinity_score(a.horizontal_fold, job_horizontal_fold)
      
      ‚üÅSek‚üÅ total_score := base_score + glyph_bonus + template_bonus + fold_bonus
      ‚üÅSek‚üÅ candidates.push({'agent': a, 'score': total_score})
  
  ‚üÅSek‚üÅ candidates.sort_by_score_desc()
  ‚üÅWo‚üÅ if candidates.length == 0
    ‚üÅWo‚üÅ return null
  
  ‚üÅWo‚üÅ return candidates[0].agent

integrated_job_pipeline_with_scxq2.kuhul_code:
‚üÅWo‚üÅ fn.micro.process_job_integrated := (job_id) -> result
  ‚üÅSek‚üÅ job := ram.table('micro_jobs_enhanced').key(job_id).get()
  ‚üÅWo‚üÅ if not job
    ‚üÅWo‚üÅ return { 'error': 'job_not_found' }
  
  # 1. Horizontal fold distribution
  ‚üÅSek‚üÅ fold_distribution := fn.horizontal_fold.distribute(job)
  ‚üÅSek‚üÅ job.horizontal_fold := fold_distribution.fold
  ‚üÅSek‚üÅ job.brain_assigned := fold_distribution.brains
  
  # 2. Glyph analysis (for SCXQ2 optimization)
  ‚üÅSek‚üÅ glyph_analysis := fn.scxq2.extract_glyphs(fn.xjson.to_string(job.input_spec))
  ‚üÅSek‚üÅ job.glyph_analysis := glyph_analysis
  
  # 3. SCXQ2-aware agent selection
  ‚üÅSek‚üÅ agent := fn.micro.select_agent_scxq2(job.domain, job.input_spec, glyph_analysis)
  ‚üÅWo‚üÅ if not agent
    ‚üÅSek‚üÅ job.status := 'error_no_agent'
    ‚üÅSek‚üÅ ram.table('micro_jobs_enhanced').key(job_id).set(job)
    ‚üÅWo‚üÅ return job
  
  # 4. Builder selection with SCXQ2 compatibility
  ‚üÅSek‚üÅ builder := fn.micro.select_builder_enhanced(agent, job.input_spec, {
    'require_scxq2': fn.should_use_scxq2(job),
    'require_horizontal_fold': true
  })
  
  # 5. MX2LM blueprint generation with multi-brain input
  ‚üÅSek‚üÅ blueprint := fn.mx2lm.generate_blueprint_enhanced(job, agent, builder, fold_distribution.brains)
  
  # 6. Builder execution (with optional SCXQ2 compression)
  ‚üÅSek‚üÅ artifact := fn.micro.execute_builder_enhanced(builder, blueprint, job, {
    'compress_with_scxq2': fn.should_compress_artifact(artifact),
    'use_horizontal_fold': true
  })
  
  # 7. Apply SCXQ2 compression if beneficial
  ‚üÅWo‚üÅ if fn.should_compress_artifact(artifact)
    ‚üÅSek‚üÅ compression_result := fn.scxq2.compress_tape(fn.xjson.to_string(artifact))
    ‚üÅSek‚üÅ job.scxq2_compressed := compression_result.compressed
    ‚üÅSek‚üÅ job.compression_ratio := compression_result.metadata.compression_ratio
    ‚üÅSek‚üÅ job.template_used := compression_result.metadata.template_used
    ‚üÅSek‚üÅ job.metrics.compression_score := 1.0 - compression_result.metadata.compression_ratio
    ‚üÅSek‚üÅ job.metrics.entropy_score := glyph_analysis.entropy
  
  # 8. Deploy with fold-aware routing
  ‚üÅSek‚üÅ deployment := fn.micro.deploy_artifact_fold_aware(artifact, builder, job, fold_distribution.fold)
  
  # 9. Update quantum state
  ‚üÅSek‚üÅ job.quantum_state := fn.quantum.capture_state({
    'agent': agent.id,
    'builder': builder.id,
    'brains': fold_distribution.brains,
    'fold': fold_distribution.fold,
    'compression_ratio': job.compression_ratio
  })
  
  # 10. Finalize job
  ‚üÅSek‚üÅ fn.finalize_job(job, agent, builder)
  
  ‚üÅWo‚üÅ return job
